Re Enron Advisory Council meeting Cc Forwarded by Vanessa GroscrandCorpEnron on AM Cindy Stark AM To Vanessa NRON cc Subject Re Enron Advisory Council meeting Vanessa Upon further review of Stans business schedule he has decided against attending the April meeting as his calendar is just really full He does still plan to attend the dinner on April Would you please amend the attendee list to reflect this and if Mr Lay or Mr Skilling have a problem with Stan not attending the meeting on the th please let us know Thanks Cindy Vanessa Groscrand PM To Cliff BaxterHOUECT Richard NRON James DerrickCorpEnron Andrew S FastowHOUECT Steven J nron Kenneth NRON Lou L ES Jeff NRON Mark FrevertNAEnron John CT Greg CT David W ES Kevin HannonEnron nron Communications Ken RiceEnron nron Communications Stan ott cc Susan SkarnessHOUECT Sharron NRON Bridget MarongeHOUECT Maureen nron Rosalee NRON Karen ES Sherri NRON Joannie NRON Lauren CT Liz M CT Kay ES CAROL nronxgate Dorothy DaltonEnron nron Communications Cindy NRON Subject Enron Advisory Council meeting Attached is the agenda for the Enron Advisory Council meeting on April Please let me know if you have any questions Vanessa

Enron Advisory Council Cc Attached is a rough draft proposed by Irwin Stelzer for the Advisory Council meeting on April You will note that Gavyn is on the agenda from pm I spoke with his assistant regarding the possibility of Gavyn departing on April and was told that he has another commitment and will need to depart the Enron Building by pm on April Also can you tell me if Prof Joe Grundfest and Lawrence Kudlow are new members of the Advisory Council I would like to update our contact list Comments please Vanessa
